er-charlie-kirk-and-erika-kirk-tpusa-successor-claims/articleshow/131360939.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/this-is-so-stupid-candace-owens-challenges-blake-neff-over-charlie-kirk-and-erika-kirk-tpusa-successor-claims/articleshow/131360939.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:57:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131360938,imgsize-2125091.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Valorant streamer GrannyGamingz reveals heartbreaking reason behind return to streaming]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131359096.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A grandmother, GrannyGamingz, is streaming Valorant to fund a headstone for her daughter, Brooke. Brooke, who passed away in 2023, had encouraged her grandmother to become a streamer. GrannyGamingz aims to honor her daughter's memory through her streams. She also seeks legal assistance to share her daughter's story. Viewers are showing strong support for her cause.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/valorant-streamer-grannygamingz-reveals-heartbreaking-reason-behind-return-to-streaming/articleshow/131359096.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/valorant-streamer-grannygamingz-reveals-heartbreaking-reason-behind-return-to-streaming/articleshow/131359096.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:04:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131359095,imgsize-195562.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Arsenal Thobe for Eid? Zohran Mamdani goes viral in bold football-themed outfit at Eid al-Adha celebration]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131358895.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Zohran Mamdani marked Eid al-Adha in the Bronx wearing a custom Arsenal-inspired thobe, blending religious tradition with football identity during a public appearance alongside Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez. The outfit, adapted from Arsenal’s away kit, drew attention online for its symbolic fusion of culture, faith and sport. Mamdani’s message on solidarity and public service framed the celebration as both personal expression and political statement in New York.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/arsenal-thobe-for-eid-zohran-mamdani-goes-viral-in-bold-football-themed-outfit-at-eid-al-adha-celebration/articleshow/131358895.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/arsenal-thobe-for-eid-zohran-mamdani-goes-viral-in-bold-football-themed-outfit-at-eid-al-adha-celebration/articleshow/131358895.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-28T03:06:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131359098,imgsize-1534098.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From Iran deal ultimatum to Ebola preparedness: Key takeaways from Donald Trump’s cabinet meeting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131358872.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-iran-talks-update-to-ebola-preparedness-key-takeaways-from-donald-trumps-cabinet-meeting/articleshow/131358872.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-iran-talks-update-to-ebola-preparedness-key-takeaways-from-donald-trumps-cabinet-meeting/articleshow/131358872.cms]]></gui